stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: SUSPECTED CRIMINAL BOTNET DOMAINS AS OF 9 AUGUST 2016
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description: AS OF 9 AUGUST 2016, UNKNOWN CRIMINAL CYBER ACTORS HAD RECONFIGURED MULTIPLE INTERNET DOMAINS FOR BOTNET OPERATIONS. THE DOMAINS HAD BEEN ASSOCIATED WITH RANSOMWARE AND OTHER KINDS OF FINANCIALLY-MOTIVATED COMPUTER INTRUSION ACTIVITY, IN THE UNITED STATES AND WORLDWIDE.
